      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="28011870">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59113592/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u59113592-8.jpg" alt="有所不为必有为" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28011870/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28011870/" class="">第40页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59113592/" class=" " title="有所不为必有为">有所不为必有为</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28011870">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">苟市民仍不输将，则吾辈亦不患无法令其出钱
孙大炮，可真是与广州同生死，呵呵</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-09 11:27</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>苟市民仍不输将，则吾辈亦不患无法令其出钱</q></blockquote>
孙大炮，可真是与广州同生死，呵呵
